## 三、Pydantic Schema 设计（替代 Dict[str, Any]）

当前项目最大的类型安全问题：所有数据流使用裸字典传递。FastAPI + Pydantic 可以彻底解决。

#### [NEW] `schemas/outline.py`
```python
from pydantic import BaseModel, Field
from typing import Optional
from enum import Enum

class LayoutType(str, Enum):
    COVER = "cover"
    TOC = "toc"
    TITLE_CONTENT = "title_content"
    TITLE_BULLETS = "title_bullets"
    TWO_COLUMN = "two_column"
    PROCESS_STEPS = "process_steps"
    ENDING = "ending"
    SECTION_TITLE = "section_title"
    # ... 其他布局类型

class PageOutline(BaseModel):
    """单页大纲 - 替代 Dict[str, Any]"""
    page_id: str = Field(default_factory=lambda: str(uuid4()))
    title: str
    points: list[str] = []
    layout_id: Optional[LayoutType] = None
    has_image: bool = False
    keywords: list[str] = []
    part: Optional[str] = None

class OutlineResponse(BaseModel):
    """大纲生成响应"""
    title: str
    pages: list[PageOutline]
```

#### [NEW] `schemas/project.py`
```python
class CreateProjectRequest(BaseModel):
    """创建项目请求 - 替代手动解析 request.json"""
    creation_type: Literal["idea", "outline", "description"]
    idea_prompt: Optional[str] = None
    outline_text: Optional[str] = None
    description_text: Optional[str] = None
    template_style: Optional[str] = None
    render_mode: Literal["image", "html"] = "image"
    scheme_id: str = "edu_dark"

class ProjectResponse(BaseModel):
    """项目响应 - 替代 project.to_dict()"""
    project_id: str
    idea_prompt: Optional[str]
    creation_type: str
    status: str
    render_mode: str
    pages: list[PageResponse] = []
    created_at: datetime
    updated_at: datetime
```

#### [NEW] `schemas/task.py`
```python
class TaskProgress(BaseModel):
    """任务进度 - 替代 JSON text 字段手动解析"""
    total: int = 0
    completed: int = 0
    failed: int = 0
    current_page: Optional[str] = None
    stage: Optional[str] = None

class TaskResponse(BaseModel):
    task_id: str
    task_type: str
    status: Literal["PENDING", "PROCESSING", "COMPLETED", "FAILED"]
    progress: TaskProgress
    error_message: Optional[str] = None
```

