## 五、关键代码模式变化

### 5.1 路由：Flask Blueprint → FastAPI Router

```diff
- # Flask (当前)
- from flask import Blueprint, request, jsonify
- project_bp = Blueprint('projects', __name__, url_prefix='/api/projects')
-
- @project_bp.route('/', methods=['POST'])
- def create_project():
-     data = request.json
-     creation_type = data.get('creation_type', 'idea')
-     idea_prompt = data.get('idea_prompt')
-     # ... 手动验证每个字段

+ # FastAPI (目标)
+ from fastapi import APIRouter, Depends
+ router = APIRouter(prefix="/api/projects", tags=["projects"])
+
+ @router.post("/", response_model=ProjectResponse)
+ async def create_project(
+     req: CreateProjectRequest,           # Pydantic 自动验证
+     db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db),  # 依赖注入
+ ):
+     # req.creation_type 自动类型检查，拼错字段直接报400
```

### 5.2 异步：ThreadPoolExecutor → async/await

```diff
- # Flask (当前) - 线程池伪并发
- self.executor = ThreadPoolExecutor(max_workers=12)
- future = self.executor.submit(generate_descriptions_task, ...)
-
- # 每个 AI 调用都占一个线程，受 GIL 限制

